metadata.name: Everything Happens for a Reason
metadata.description:
3D Digital  
3750 x 5000 (pixel)  
Edition 1/2  
2022

The eternal ring in the world somewhere entices the Consciousness. Countless predecessors and future people to come and they inevitably realize the truth - the present is mixed with past, future and eternity. The broken ring is also a reconstruction and a deconstruction simultaneously.
